<p>On the palate, expect concentrated dark fruit flavors supported by earthy undertones of graphite, cedar, and dried herbs. Spice notes include black pepper, clove, and subtle baking spices from oak integration. The <strong>finish</strong> in quality Bordeaux extends for 30-45 seconds or more, leaving impressions of dark chocolate, espresso, and mineral dust.</p>

